data.description: Welcome to a home that combines the tranquility of country living with the convenience of living in the city! This property offers a main area with 2bedrooms, 1 1/2 baths, a large eat-in kitchen, a separate living room and a laundry area. One of the standout features is the in-law suite, which can be used aa master suite, or an accommodation for your live-in parents. This versatile space boasts a kitchenette, a walk-in closet, a private bath with a walk-in shower, and a separate entrance for added privacy. Step outside into the fenced-in rear backyard, complete with a covered patio. Great for enjoying outdoor activities, entertaining guests, or simply unwinding after a long day. Additional storage space is provided by two spacious outbuildings, ensuring you have plenty of room for all your belongings. This home features a charming brick front, a metal roof and a unique opportunity with the separate suite. Schedule a showing today and experience the unique charm of this property for yourself!
